DestroyMenu MenuSendTo
AddToMenu MenuSendTo
+ "$[gt.Current]" MoveToCurrent
+ "$[gt.Page]" PopUp MenuSendToPage
+ "$[gt.Desk]" PopUp MenuSendToDesk

DestroyMenu MenuSendToDesk
